name: DAG Confirm Parallel
version: 1.0.0
max_parallel: 2
---

# DAG Confirm Parallel

Two independent steps that each open a confirmation gate. When the
scheduler dispatches them concurrently, the prompt mutex must
serialise the two prompts so their stderr output does not interleave.

```step name="alpha"
  confirm: always
---
echo "alpha ran"
```

```step name="beta"
  confirm: always
---
echo "beta ran"
```
